(the bullet might have hit his head.)

36
00:02:32,879 --> 00:02:33,840
Mr. Cai.

37
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,680
Such things

38
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:39,800
can be pre-arranged.

39
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,560
Right?

40
00:02:45,039 --> 00:02:46,240
Isn't it

41
