47
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,159
I didn't tell you.

48
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,800
Now I'll tell you.

49
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,840
The mission regarding Huang Zhixing

50
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,960
is already completed.

51
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,879
I knew I'd

52
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,000
encounter many situations.

53
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:33,039
But I didn't expect

54
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,919
to shoot our people.

55
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,840
Tianshuang.

56
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,280
You did very well.

57
00:04:09,479 --> 00:04:11,120
But now we don't even know

58
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,080
if he's alive.

59
00:04:12,919 --> 00:04:13,800
Don't worry.

60
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,360
He'll make it.

61
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,360
Shooting Huang Zhixing?

62
00:04:21,199 --> 00:04:22,279
Chief Xu said

63
