it was Huang Zhixing's own request.

64
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:25,680
But why?

65
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,600
Zheng Taixiang was quite wary of him.

66
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:29,920
And the intel on the Eye Plan
isn't easy to get.

67
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,160
He'll put on a show.

68
00:04:31,759 --> 00:04:34,199
He'll deliberately fall
into Zheng Taixiang's trap.

69
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:35,199
When Zheng Taixiang

70
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:36,600
