about the Eye Plan.

74
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:43,360
Others?

75
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,720
Even if it's to attract attention,

76
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,199
I don't need to shoot him.

77
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:51,000
The Agency is searching for spies.

78
00:04:51,600 --> 00:04:52,519
He decided

79
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,240
to turn their game against them.

80
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:56,839
He'll deliberately fail to escape

81
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:58,079
