85
00:05:02,959 --> 00:05:04,040
The real mole

86
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,160
is Zheng Taixiang.

87
00:05:05,639 --> 00:05:07,000
And then, you can shoot him.

88
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,360
So,

89
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,199
Cai Desheng believes

90
00:05:10,199 --> 00:05:11,439
Taixiang wants Zhixing gone?

91
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:12,519
Yes.

92
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,600
That's too risky.

93
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,040
Complete the mission.

94
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,839
The gun is prepared for you.

95
00:05:30,879 --> 00:05:32,439
The location is at the damaged railing.

96
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,800
Huang Zhixing said

97
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,600
he'd pause here,

98
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:02,720
step forward,

99
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,879
