No.

104
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,040
The distance is too far.

105
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,959
The wind is strong.

106
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,680
When he stumbles,

107
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:17,160
his posture is uncontrollable.

108
00:06:17,519 --> 00:06:18,920
Who can guarantee

109
00:06:19,680 --> 00:06:20,600
I'll hit his shoulder?

110
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,639
How can I be sure?

111
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,000
I know it's difficult.

112
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:24,920
But Huang Zhixing said,

113
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,560
if we back out,

114
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,040
he'll do it himself.

115
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:30,000
It's okay if I shoot crooked.

116
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,079
But what if I really

117
00:06:31,079 --> 00:06:32,279
hit his head?

118
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,800
Huang Zhixing said

119
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,360
