291
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:22,000
(Until today,)

292
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:24,480
(I still can't say I agree with my dad.)

293
00:15:25,279 --> 00:15:26,320
(After all,)

294
00:15:26,320 --> 00:15:27,720
(I grew up in a completely)

