00:15:52,559 --> 00:15:53,960
(as enemies?)

304
00:15:58,694 --> 00:16:03,332
♪We search along the way♪

305
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:07,120
(In his view,)

306
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:08,480
(the compatriots are family,)

307
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:09,679
(not enemies.)

308
00:16:11,879 --> 00:16:13,080
(I think so.)

309
00:16:15,159 --> 00:16:16,879
(There are always people
who like to say)

310
00:16:16,879 --> 00:16:19,039
(that Taiwan, China, needs to control
its own future.)

311
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:22,000
(This is a beautiful wish.)

312
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:24,240
(But when you have seen the world,)

313
00:16:24,240 --> 00:16:26,960
(you'll find that the world is not
a series of isolated islands.)

314
00:16:27,559 --> 00:16:29,559
(They are interconnected.)

315
00:16:33,679 --> 00:16:34,639
Hello, Mr. Huang.

316
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:37,480
Who are you?

317
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:38,720
Don't be nervous.

318
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:40,159
I mean no harm.

319
00:16:41,759 --> 00:16:42,759
We know

320
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:45,080
you care about cross-strait relations.

321
00:16:45,519 --> 00:16:46,399
In the future,

322
00:16:46,399 --> 00:16:47,759
if you need help with anything

323
00:16:47,759 --> 00:16:48,799
or encounter danger,

324
00:16:48,799 --> 00:16:50,120
you can contact us.

325
00:16:51,080 --> 00:16:52,600
Just consider it as making a friend.

326
