338
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,440
(Doing these things)

339
00:17:37,759 --> 00:17:40,400
(made me accustomed to keeping
everything bottled up inside.)

340
00:17:41,359 --> 00:17:43,359
(Until one day, my wife told me)

341
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:46,799
(she could no longer bear
my indifference.)

342
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:49,400
(She wanted a divorce.)

343
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:51,599
(I understood her choice.)

344
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:53,279
Are we going to remain silent like this?

345
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:56,000
Can you tell me

346
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,160
