347
00:17:58,799 --> 00:17:59,920
Huang Zhixing, you...

348
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:04,440
I'm taking Xi to the zoo on Sunday.

349
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:05,400
Will you come along?

350
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:09,039
I really have no time.

351
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,759
No time?

352
00:18:12,119 --> 00:18:13,240
No time?

353
00:18:13,759 --> 00:18:16,079
When exactly will you have time?

354
00:18:16,279 --> 00:18:17,680
You come back so late every night.

355
00:18:17,680 --> 00:18:18,880
What do you do? With whom?

356
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:19,519
Keep it down.

357
00:18:19,519 --> 00:18:20,680
Why should I?

358
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,799
How do you expect me to?

359
00:18:22,799 --> 00:18:24,039
Xi is sleeping.

360
00:18:24,799 --> 00:18:26,680
I really can't communicate with you.

361
00:18:26,680 --> 00:18:27,880
Are you still doing this?

362
00:18:33,830 --> 00:18:37,640
