364
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,960
(So every time I see my daughter,)

365
00:18:42,480 --> 00:18:43,519
(I always treat it)

366
00:18:43,519 --> 00:18:44,720
(as the last time.)

367
00:18:46,759 --> 00:18:48,920
