371
00:18:55,599 --> 00:18:58,119
(I feel that if I can
make any contribution,)

372
00:18:58,119 --> 00:18:59,640
(I shouldn't hold back.)

373
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:02,880
(Safety)

374
00:19:02,880 --> 00:19:04,880
(is an illusion.)

375
00:19:05,480 --> 00:19:07,799
(I won't let air raid sirens)

376
00:19:08,359 --> 00:19:10,920
(War brings suffering to civilians)
(haunt Xi's childhood.)

377
00:19:13,440 --> 00:19:15,359
(Her peace)

378
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:18,200
(is worth any sacrifice.)
